title: Start
body:
<<Speaking Morgan>> Hey Lucy, how's it going?

[[Pretty good.|101t]]
[[I'm fine.|101t]]

title: 101t
body:
That's good. 
She looks you up and down. 
Are you, uh, going to wear that to the party?

[[Oh... yea.|201t]]
[[I was planning on it.|202t]]

title: 201t
body:
I hate to nitpick and everything, but that outfit isn't really right for this kind of party, haha. 
It's sort of a bit more... high class, you know?

[[Oh, okay.|301t]]
[[Oh shit, I'm sorry.|302t]]

title: 301t
body:
Yea, I mean, you don't have to change if you don't want to, but you know, you should look your best, you know? 
You're a star, and you deserve to shine.

[[Okay, I'll go change.|401t]]
[[I'll be right back.|401t]]

title: 302t
body:
Oh no, don't apologize! Everyone I know is always apologizing for things.
Instead of saying stuff like "I'm sorry I complain so much," say stuff like, "Thank you so much for listening to me."
It makes people feel better about themselves!

[[I never thought of that.|addedt]]
[[Wow, you're right!|addedt]]

title: addedt
body:
